===Pronunciation===
*שׁירה  /  שׁיר
*shîyr  shîyrâh / sheer, shee-raw'

===Etymology===
The second form being feminine; from {{HH|7891}}; 

===Noun===
'''שׁיר'''

# a [[song]]; abstractly singing: - musical (-ick), X sing (-er, -ing), song.

